Let’s jump into Sunday like @queenofthebus and @icantseecasper jump into this performance! 💃🏽🤸🏾‍♀️💥

Join us today for our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm
Our Sunday T Dance at 6pm at the PALACE Cafe
And our evening shows from 7-1130pm

node.text:
It’s Friday and we’re ready to get the weekend started!! 
Let’s celebrate together, starting with our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm, let’s grab a delicious drink on our rooftop and then continue the fun with our evening shows from 7-1130pm 🙌🏽💥💃🏽💃🏽

One of our dancing queens @tiara_love_dupree performing @kelis

It’s Thursday and we’re ready for some #CafeConLeche at PALACE from 7-1130pm
Our talented queens bring you great looks to great music- while you enjoy the shows with some food, drinks and hookahs! 
Join us and let’s celebrate!💃🏽💥

node.accessibility_caption:
What a great start to the weekend!
